was amazing and super helpful, for being my first time they were patient and all their suggestions were on point.  The pistachio and Nutella dipped cone was worth the money! The crema Torino ice cream was definitely my favorite 😍", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "10/10 The staff here was amazing and super helpful, for being my first time they were patient and all their suggestions were on point.  The pistachio and Nutella dipped cone was worth the money! The crema Torino ice cream was definitely my favorite 😍", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "John Ortiz", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110257822405757488130/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaArcupPSfevmFi12GKl9NlNZ-ZZAxGYCjufO1bK1WAPV9Wg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-08T06:28:18.354110638Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkcFRVNVNSMDkxTVRWeWIwWldWVGR4UzNrMVRsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkcFRVNVNSMDkxTVRWeWIwWldWVGR4UzNrMVRsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3f2482c2b1f:0x90d66812c18c8493"}, {"name": "places/ChIJHyssSPLDwoARk4SMwRJo1pA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoU2RUSlJPVUZ5VnpOdE5DMHdWbnBvTlZJMGVHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Best gelato in town. Loved the waffle with strawberry gelato so much I bought a second one to take home. A Pasadena must try.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Best gelato in town. Loved the waffle with strawberry gelato so much I bought a second one to take home. A Pasadena must try.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tiegrun", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112093846225839407732/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPL3WeQ18tVtqV6i219Qt-AFT7ktV4oAgNHZEQQbEQMS7CRm8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-15T04:21:11.815607279Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoU2RUSlJPVUZ5VnpOdE5DMHdWbnBvTlZJMGVHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoU2RUSlJPVUZ5VnpOdE5DMHdWbnBvTlZJMGVHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3f2482c2b1f:0x90d66812c18c8493"}, {"name": "places/ChIJHyssSPLDwoARk4SMwRJo1pA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psdGRrVXpWbDlTUTI5T1ZHdzJPREJDWjFKVVVXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The Gelato is just amazing, so tasty and authentic. Definitely not cheap but really worth the price. 3 Chocolates and Chocolate Pistachio Crunch were just heaven. So many good flavours, hard to pick some...", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The Gelato is just amazing, so tasty and authentic. Definitely not cheap but really worth the price. 3 Chocolates and Chocolate Pistachio Crunch were just heaven. So many good flavours, hard to pick some...", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sandra Rosenkranz", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105892451061193642650/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiIP1w5csDlphHwtgBW3nk2X6KgpsQ4N4f558Bz-Oz--hNIlw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-06T03:39:28.028627060Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psdGRrVXpWbDlTUTI5T1ZHdzJPREJDWjFKVVVXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psdGRrVXpWbDlTUTI5T1ZHdzJPREJDWjFKVVVXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3f2482c2b1f:0x90d66812c18c8493"}, {"name": "places/ChIJHyssSPLDwoARk4SMwRJo1pA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xdFN6aHdlSEpXYjJVM1YyMHhRbXRvVHpCTFNtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I’m not sure why this place does not have five stars yet on Google reviews but it should! They just opened the Pasadena location Christmas 2024 so it’s been about 7 months since it’s Grand Opening. You pay for what you get. It is truly worth $10. I ordered 2 flavors - their Mousse di Pistacchio and Rosa & Vaniglia (paying homage to the “City of Roses”) in their fresh and warm waffle cone coated with oozing pistachio cream. There’s so much hard work, effort, and high-quality ingredients put into each and every flavor. Every single flavor is absolutely mesmerizing. How do I know? You are able to sample as many flavors as you like! I hate getting turned down by other ice cream shops that do not allow customers to sample flavors. How will you know what you like? Those places make it into a game of gambling. On the other hand, I am really grateful for the generous sampling culture at Bacio di Latte. That small gesture instills trust, loyalty, and respect towards the customer.\n\nFurthermore, I am not a chocolate lover, but I absolutely adore all the chocolate hazelnut variety they have. Truly, Bacio di Latte elevates you to 7th heaven and makes you reminisce the Italian dolce vita. Their gelato chain is true gem here in LA. It’s definitely a special way to treat yourself or even end a romantic date. They prioritize quality by using one of the best local milk companies, Clover Sonoma, in order to perfect their gelato. You will definitely experience a food high after coming here - especially if you have a little ice cream obsession! I’m definitely going to be a regular here!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’m not sure why this place does not have five stars yet on Google reviews but it should! They just opened the Pasadena location Christmas 2024 so it’s been about 7 months since it’s Grand Opening. You pay for what you get. It is truly worth $10. I ordered 2 flavors - their Mousse di Pistacchio and Rosa & Vaniglia (paying homage to the “City of Roses”) in their fresh and warm waffle cone coated with oozing pistachio cream. There’s so much hard work, effort, and high-quality ingredients put into each and every flavor. Every single flavor is absolutely mesmerizing. How do I know? You are able to sample as many flavors as you like! I hate getting turned down by other ice cream shops that do not allow customers to sample flavors. How will you know what you like? Those places make it into a game of gambling. On the other hand, I am really grateful for the generous sampling culture at Bacio di Latte. That small gesture instills trust, loyalty, and respect towards the customer.\n\nFurthermore, I am not a chocolate lover, but I absolutely adore all the chocolate hazelnut variety they have. Truly, Bacio di Latte elevates you to 7th heaven and makes you reminisce the Italian dolce vita. Their gelato chain is true gem here in LA. It’s definitely a special way to treat yourself or even end a romantic date. They prioritize quality by using one of the best local milk companies, Clover Sonoma, in order to perfect their gelato. You will definitely experience a food high after coming here - especially if you have a little ice cream obsession! I’m definitely going to be a regular here!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Uberrimaefidei", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110548149540907828038/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLW4-8PLamA5rKxYtLrJBdfHxoN5OLdhqObBkPXIfDemK_1-w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-07-13T23:53:39.498137476Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xdFN6aHdlSEpXYjJVM1YyMHhRbXRvVHpCTFNtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xdFN6aHdlSEpXYjJVM1YyMHhRbXRvVHpCTFNtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3f2482c2b1f:0x90d66812c18c8493"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJHyssSPLDwoARk4SMwRJo1pA/photos